I think there is a misunderstanding, my suggestion:
```python
def list_sources(owner=None, page=None, page_size=None):
    '''List all harvest sources'''
    sources = HarvestSource.objects.visible()
    if owner:
        sources = sources.owned_by(owner)
    if page_size:
        page = max(page or 1, 1)
        sources = sources.paginate(page, page_size)
    return list(sources)
```
